1
00:00:01,001 --> 00:00:02,252
[MILA] <i>Lucas.</i>

2
00:00:02,335 --> 00:00:05,255
<i>Tell Boss Emil that you have</i>
<i>to leave the building now.</i>

3
00:00:05,338 --> 00:00:07,549
[LUNA] <i>You're with the hostage takers.</i>

4
00:00:07,632 --> 00:00:08,967
<i>Admit it!</i>

5
00:00:09,050 --> 00:00:10,051
[LUNA GROANS]

6
00:00:10,135 --> 00:00:11,761
- [IVAN] <i>Police!</i>
- [LUNA] <i>Doc!</i>

7
00:00:11,845 --> 00:00:15,974
[LUCAS] <i>That was Mila.</i>
<i>She said we need to get out of here now.</i>

8
00:00:16,057 --> 00:00:17,976
<i>- Why?</i>
<i>- She didn't say.</i>

9
00:00:18,059 --> 00:00:20,562
<i>Any mistake could put</i>
<i>the hostages at risk.</i>

10
00:00:20,645 --> 00:00:21,521
<i>We won't make a mistake.</i>

11
00:00:21,604 --> 00:00:23,523
<i>- And when they take the bait?</i>
- [AREZA]<i> We'll move.</i>

12
00:00:23,606 --> 00:00:25,442
<i>We'll go straight for their leader.</i>

13
00:00:25,525 --> 00:00:28,069
<i>You still don't know me.</i>

14
00:00:28,153 --> 00:00:30,447
<i>My rules are simple.</i>

15
00:00:30,530 --> 00:00:32,449
<i>If someone makes a mistake</i>
<i>or commits a sin,</i>

16
00:00:32,532 --> 00:00:33,575
<i>they will be punished.</i>

17
00:00:33,658 --> 00:00:34,534
- [GUNSHOT]
<i>- Ma!</i>

18
00:00:35,160 --> 00:00:36,244
- [GUNSHOT]
<i>- Boss!</i>

19
00:00:36,327 --> 00:00:38,455
- [COCKS RIFLE]
<i>- Let's get out of here!</i>

20
00:00:38,997 --> 00:00:40,206
<i>You can't escape!</i>

21
00:00:40,290 --> 00:00:41,458
<i>We'll blow you up!</i>

22
00:00:41,541 --> 00:00:43,376
[MACKY GRUNTS, SCOFFS]

23
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:45,295
<i>- Let's go! Come on!</i>
<i>- Hurry!</i>

24
00:00:45,837 --> 00:00:47,547
<i>Give me your gun, Homer! Come on!</i>

25
00:00:48,465 --> 00:00:50,675
<i>I'll kill him! What, Pa?! Come on!</i>

26
00:00:52,552 --> 00:00:54,262
[GUNSHOTS]

27
00:00:55,263 --> 00:00:56,514
[INDISTINCT SHOUTING]

28
00:00:57,223 --> 00:00:58,933
[RAPID GUNFIRE]

29
00:01:02,062 --> 00:01:04,564
[EMIL] <i>Homer, don't let your son get away!</i>

30
00:01:04,647 --> 00:01:05,857
[HOMER] <i>Yes, boss.</i>

31
00:01:06,274 --> 00:01:07,567
[EMIL] <i>Go after Magnus!</i>

32
00:01:07,650 --> 00:01:09,194
<i>I need him alive.</i>

33
00:01:09,277 --> 00:01:10,612
<i>Yes, sir.</i>

34
00:01:10,695 --> 00:01:14,157
<i>Take Leni to the basement now!</i>

35
00:01:14,240 --> 00:01:15,950
[JACINTO] <i>I'm not the mastermind</i>

36
00:01:16,034 --> 00:01:18,745
<i>of the hostage taking at La Playa Roja.</i>

37
00:01:18,828 --> 00:01:21,956
<i>Greta Roja is the real mastermind</i>

38
00:01:22,040 --> 00:01:24,209
<i>of the hostage taking at La Playa Roja.</i>

39
00:01:24,292 --> 00:01:27,629
[JACINTO, VIDEO] <i>I'll give you your share.</i>
<i>Ten times the investment.</i>

40
00:01:27,712 --> 00:01:29,589
What happened?
The bomb didn't explode?

41
00:01:29,672 --> 00:01:31,341
Macky found the transmitter.

42
00:01:31,424 --> 00:01:33,718
He destroyed it so the bombs
wouldn't explode anymore.

43
00:01:33,802 --> 00:01:35,470
Aunt Wendy, where's Papa?

44
00:01:35,553 --> 00:01:36,554
On the rooftop.

45
00:01:36,638 --> 00:01:37,931
With Olsen!

46
00:01:38,014 --> 00:01:39,849
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [GROANS]

47
00:01:39,933 --> 00:01:42,060
[MACKY] Dad! Dad!

48
00:01:42,143 --> 00:01:44,103
- Dad!
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]

49
00:01:44,187 --> 00:01:47,232
[GLUM MUSIC PLAYING]

50
00:01:47,315 --> 00:01:49,692
Please, help Macky!

51
00:01:49,776 --> 00:01:52,028
Men! Evacuate the hostages! Let's move!

52
00:01:52,112 --> 00:01:53,988
- [OFFICER] Move! Move!
- Let's get out of here.

53
00:01:54,072 --> 00:01:55,824
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]
- [GUNSHOTS]

54
00:01:57,283 --> 00:01:58,243
Freeze!

55
00:01:59,035 --> 00:02:04,374
[GUNSHOTS]

56
00:02:04,457 --> 00:02:06,751
- [MACKY] Dad!
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]

57
00:02:08,461 --> 00:02:10,547
Let go of me! [GROANS]

58
00:02:11,548 --> 00:02:13,466
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA WHIMPERS]
- [MACKY] Dad!

59
00:02:13,550 --> 00:02:15,135
[OFFICER] Medic! Medic!

60
00:02:15,218 --> 00:02:18,138
- Dad! It's gonna be okay.
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]

61
00:02:18,221 --> 00:02:22,267
- Oh my God! [GROANS]
- It's going to be okay.

62
00:02:22,350 --> 00:02:23,810
[KEEPS GROANING]

63
00:02:31,442 --> 00:02:38,449
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]

64
00:03:10,440 --> 00:03:12,358
[GUNSHOTS]

65
00:03:12,442 --> 00:03:13,610
[PANICKED BREATHING]

66
00:03:13,693 --> 00:03:15,737
[GUNSHOTS]

67
00:03:23,286 --> 00:03:26,039
[GUNSHOTS]

68
00:03:28,499 --> 00:03:29,709
[RIFLE COCKS]

69
00:03:29,792 --> 00:03:34,839
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

70
00:03:40,303 --> 00:03:41,721
[OLSEN SHOUTS]

71
00:03:43,181 --> 00:03:45,433
[OLSEN, HOMER GRUNTING]

72
00:03:54,192 --> 00:03:55,485
- [HOMER GRUNTS]
- [OLSEN GROANS]

73
00:03:55,985 --> 00:03:58,279
- [OFFICER] Hey!
- [GUNSHOTS]

74
00:03:58,363 --> 00:04:03,159
[GUNSHOTS]

75
00:04:04,786 --> 00:04:07,372
- [OFFICER] Are you okay?
- Follow him! Go!

76
00:04:07,997 --> 00:04:09,540
[OLSEN] Just go!

77
00:04:09,624 --> 00:04:11,042
Go after him!

78
00:04:22,804 --> 00:04:28,935
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

79
00:04:44,784 --> 00:04:51,791
[UNSETTLING MUSIC CONTINUES]

80
00:04:54,002 --> 00:04:55,461
[LUCAS GRUNTS]

81
00:04:56,504 --> 00:05:00,883
[LUCAS, MAGNUS GRUNTING]

82
00:05:07,932 --> 00:05:09,058
Come on!

83
00:05:09,142 --> 00:05:10,226
Come at me!

84
00:05:11,269 --> 00:05:13,855
[LUCAS, MAGNUS GRUNTING]

85
00:05:13,938 --> 00:05:18,276
[BOTH GRUNTING,
BLOWS LANDING]

86
00:05:19,652 --> 00:05:21,738
[LUCAS YELLS]

87
00:05:21,821 --> 00:05:23,990
[MAGNUS GROANS]

88
00:05:24,073 --> 00:05:25,033
[LUCAS GRUNTS]

89
00:05:25,116 --> 00:05:26,200
[OFFICER] Hey!

90
00:05:26,284 --> 00:05:29,037
- [GUNSHOTS]
- [MAGNUS GROANING]

91
00:05:29,120 --> 00:05:33,624
[GUNSHOTS]

92
00:05:37,128 --> 00:05:39,881
[MAGNUS GROANS]

93
00:05:39,964 --> 00:05:41,340
Save everyone here inside.

94
00:05:41,424 --> 00:05:42,925
Tell them to be careful.

95
00:05:43,009 --> 00:05:44,385
Yes, sir.

96
00:05:44,469 --> 00:05:46,012
- This way, sir.
- [LIAM] Let's go.

97
00:05:46,095 --> 00:05:52,143
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

98
00:05:56,981 --> 00:05:58,691
Enough.

99
00:06:12,330 --> 00:06:14,874
Boss Emil. The police are here.

100
00:06:20,671 --> 00:06:21,672
[EMIL GRUNTS]

101
00:06:21,756 --> 00:06:27,303
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

102
00:06:27,386 --> 00:06:28,513
[GROANS]

103
00:06:29,097 --> 00:06:30,515
[EXHALES DEEPLY]

104
00:06:35,186 --> 00:06:36,312
[DADO] Let's go, Fredo!

105
00:06:37,855 --> 00:06:38,940
[DADO] Come on!

106
00:06:39,440 --> 00:06:42,902
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

107
00:06:48,241 --> 00:06:49,575
[OLSEN] Sir! Sir!

108
00:06:49,659 --> 00:06:50,910
Sir…
[EXHALES DEEPLY]

109
00:06:50,993 --> 00:06:52,328
- Are you okay?
- [OLSEN] Sir.

110
00:06:52,411 --> 00:06:54,205
W-Where's Mama?

111
00:06:54,288 --> 00:06:56,124
And the other hostages? Where are they?

112
00:06:56,874 --> 00:06:58,167
They were already evacuated.

113
00:06:58,251 --> 00:06:59,919
[OLSEN] Okay… Okay.

114
00:07:00,002 --> 00:07:05,007
Sir Mike, Ms. Minnie, and their daughter
are probably still here.

115
00:07:05,091 --> 00:07:06,592
They got separated from us.

116
00:07:09,053 --> 00:07:15,351
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

117
00:07:15,435 --> 00:07:19,188
I don't know what it is,
but they were tasked to do something.

118
00:07:19,272 --> 00:07:23,234
We have to get to them first
before Emil Padua does.

119
00:07:25,069 --> 00:07:27,488
- [RADIO WHIRS]
- Attention, all units.

120
00:07:28,072 --> 00:07:31,033
There are still hostages
that we haven't found.

121
00:07:31,117 --> 00:07:32,827
The Del Rosario family.

122
00:07:32,910 --> 00:07:34,287
There are three of them.

123
00:07:34,370 --> 00:07:37,248
Clear all the areas and be alert.

124
00:07:37,331 --> 00:07:40,710
Some hostages and hostage takers
may still be here in the building.

125
00:07:42,545 --> 00:07:43,379
Men.

126
00:07:44,589 --> 00:07:45,882
Bring Olsen outside.

127
00:07:47,133 --> 00:07:48,259
[OLSEN GRUNTS]

128
00:07:48,342 --> 00:07:53,514
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

129
00:07:55,391 --> 00:07:56,726
[PANTING]

130
00:07:57,768 --> 00:07:58,895
- [EMIL GRUNTS]
- [DADO] Boss?

131
00:07:58,978 --> 00:08:00,605
- [EMIL GRUNTING]
- [DADO] Boss!

132
00:08:00,688 --> 00:08:03,316
- [GROANING] Dado!
- [DADO] Get a gun!

133
00:08:04,066 --> 00:08:05,234
- Boss.
- [EMIL GRUNTS]

134
00:08:06,903 --> 00:08:09,489
- [EMIL GROANS SHARPLY]
- [DADO STRAINING]

135
00:08:10,156 --> 00:08:11,532
- Let's go!
- Can you walk, boss?

136
00:08:11,616 --> 00:08:13,993
I can do it! Come on!

137
00:08:14,076 --> 00:08:15,912
[DADO] Fredo, let's go!

138
00:08:17,330 --> 00:08:20,124
[EMIL GRUNTS]

139
00:08:21,876 --> 00:08:24,962
[PHONE BUZZING, BEEPS]

140
00:08:27,131 --> 00:08:28,508
What's the status of the operation?

141
00:08:28,591 --> 00:08:31,802
Sir. We've already evacuated
some of the hostages.

142
00:08:32,553 --> 00:08:35,181
The search is still ongoing
to evacuate the others.

143
00:08:35,264 --> 00:08:38,059
What about Senator Eduardo and his son?

144
00:08:38,142 --> 00:08:39,769
The senator got shot, sir.

145
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:42,104
He's being tended to.

146
00:08:42,897 --> 00:08:44,398
What about the hostage takers?

147
00:08:44,482 --> 00:08:47,109
Our men are chasing after them, sir.

148
00:08:47,193 --> 00:08:51,864
I have people guarding the entrances
and exits so they can't escape.

149
00:08:51,948 --> 00:08:53,616
What about Greta Roja?

150
00:08:53,699 --> 00:08:55,910
She's one of the first hostages
who was evacuated, sir.

151
00:08:58,079 --> 00:08:58,913
Why?

152
00:08:58,996 --> 00:09:00,498
She can't escape.

153
00:09:01,582 --> 00:09:02,416
Sir?

154
00:09:02,500 --> 00:09:04,085
Alert all men.

155
00:09:04,168 --> 00:09:05,920
We need to arrest Greta Roja.

156
00:09:06,003 --> 00:09:11,676
[STIRRING MUSIC PLAYING]

157
00:09:13,302 --> 00:09:14,136
[GRETA] Liam!

158
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:32,697
[DARK MUSIC PLAYING]

159
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,954
[EMIL GRUNTING]

160
00:09:44,333 --> 00:09:46,919
[EMIL GRUNTING]

161
00:09:48,879 --> 00:09:50,840
- [EMIL GROANS SHARPLY]
- Hang in there, boss.

162
00:09:50,923 --> 00:09:53,301
[EMIL KEEPS GROANING]

163
00:09:53,384 --> 00:09:57,388
- [DADO] Lucas!
- [LUCAS] Boss Emil! Boss Emil.

164
00:09:58,014 --> 00:09:59,640
- Are you okay?
- I'll be fine.

165
00:09:59,724 --> 00:10:01,767
- [DADO] Ready?
- [LUCAS] Let's go.

166
00:10:01,851 --> 00:10:03,603
- Dado.
- [DADO] Let's go.

167
00:10:04,437 --> 00:10:07,773
[EMIL KEEPS GROANING]

168
00:10:15,323 --> 00:10:21,162
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

169
00:10:24,332 --> 00:10:30,755
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

170
00:10:39,221 --> 00:10:43,684
- [SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]
- [HURRIED FOOTSTEPS]

171
00:10:43,768 --> 00:10:45,019
Clear!

172
00:10:45,102 --> 00:10:47,146
- [OFFICER 1] Clear!
- [OFFICER 2] All clear!

173
00:10:48,522 --> 00:10:54,987
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

174
00:11:05,331 --> 00:11:06,332
[AREZA] Men.

175
00:11:09,460 --> 00:11:15,716
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

176
00:11:22,556 --> 00:11:23,724
[LUCAS] Go!

177
00:11:24,433 --> 00:11:26,310
[EMIL GROANS]

178
00:11:27,311 --> 00:11:32,983
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [EMIL GROANING]

179
00:11:40,282 --> 00:11:46,622
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

180
00:11:57,758 --> 00:12:04,098
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

181
00:12:26,495 --> 00:12:27,705
Men.

182
00:12:27,788 --> 00:12:29,540
Take this as evidence.

183
00:12:33,377 --> 00:12:39,967
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

184
00:12:55,858 --> 00:12:57,818
[GRETA] No! I'm not leaving!

185
00:12:57,902 --> 00:13:00,279
- What about your father?
- Liam, where's Olsen?

186
00:13:00,362 --> 00:13:02,573
Ma, Aunt Wendy, I'll find them, okay?

187
00:13:02,656 --> 00:13:03,574
Go.

188
00:13:03,657 --> 00:13:10,498
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

189
00:13:10,581 --> 00:13:14,001
[REPORTER] <i>Captain Jericho Jacinto</i>
<i>identified Greta Roja</i>

190
00:13:14,084 --> 00:13:17,963
<i>as the mastermind of the hostage taking</i>
<i>that took place at La Playa Roja.</i>

191
00:13:18,047 --> 00:13:21,300
<i>According to Jacinto,</i>
<i>they have evidence to support this claim.</i>

192
00:13:21,383 --> 00:13:22,927
<i>They have video footage</i>

193
00:13:23,010 --> 00:13:27,723
<i>that will prove Greta Roja's involvement</i>
<i>in the bloody hostage taking incident.</i>

194
00:13:27,806 --> 00:13:32,228
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

195
00:13:32,311 --> 00:13:34,647
[GRETA] <i>Hello? Jericho?</i>

196
00:13:34,730 --> 00:13:37,525
<i>Ma. Who were you talking to?</i>

197
00:13:37,608 --> 00:13:39,109
<i>Who's Jericho?</i>

198
00:13:39,902 --> 00:13:42,696
<i>He's-- He's my contact</i>
<i>at the police station.</i>

199
00:13:42,780 --> 00:13:45,824
<i>Liam, he's our ally!</i>
<i>You have to believe me!</i>

200
00:13:45,908 --> 00:13:47,576
<i>Don't trust him, Ma!</i>

201
00:13:48,244 --> 00:13:49,453
[JERICHO] <i>Greta.</i>

202
00:13:49,537 --> 00:13:51,830
<i>Explain everything to your son!</i>

203
00:13:51,914 --> 00:13:54,208
<i>He's the mastermind.</i>

204
00:13:54,291 --> 00:13:56,794
<i>The real boss of all of us.</i>

205
00:13:56,877 --> 00:13:57,795
<i>It's not me.</i>

206
00:14:00,506 --> 00:14:05,844
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

207
00:14:05,928 --> 00:14:09,181
- [TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [POLICE SHOUT UNINTELLIGIBLY BELOW]

208
00:14:09,265 --> 00:14:10,224
[MACKY] Help!

209
00:14:10,808 --> 00:14:12,601
- Careful! [GROANS]
- There they are!

210
00:14:12,685 --> 00:14:14,853
- Let's go to them.
- Help, please!

211
00:14:14,937 --> 00:14:16,897
- Mister, help!
- We need help!

212
00:14:16,981 --> 00:14:20,025
- He's badly injured.
- Hurry, help him.

213
00:14:20,109 --> 00:14:22,069
- He's bleeding!
- [MACKY] Help!

214
00:14:22,152 --> 00:14:23,362
[SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANS]

215
00:14:23,445 --> 00:14:24,738
- He was shot.
- Be careful.

216
00:14:24,822 --> 00:14:26,198
- I applied pressure.
- Ow.

217
00:14:26,282 --> 00:14:27,366
I tried. I tried.

218
00:14:27,449 --> 00:14:28,701
- Hurry!
- Move!

219
00:14:28,784 --> 00:14:29,702
[GROANS]

220
00:14:29,785 --> 00:14:31,745
- This way.
- Let's go.

221
00:14:31,829 --> 00:14:34,623
- [MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]
- [SENATOR MARISTELLA GROANING]

222
00:14:34,707 --> 00:14:41,672
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC PLAYING]

223
00:14:45,885 --> 00:14:47,011
[DOOR OPENS]

224
00:14:47,094 --> 00:14:48,012
[OFFICER] Clear!

225
00:14:48,095 --> 00:14:54,643
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

226
00:15:00,399 --> 00:15:01,400
[DOOR OPENS]

227
00:15:02,192 --> 00:15:03,110
[OFFICER] Clear!

228
00:15:03,193 --> 00:15:10,159
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

229
00:15:14,455 --> 00:15:21,462
[SUSPENSEFUL MUSIC CONTINUES]

230
00:15:27,343 --> 00:15:28,636
[WIRE SNAPS]

231
00:15:30,095 --> 00:15:32,348
[BOMB TICKING]

232
00:15:32,431 --> 00:15:33,432
[WIRE SNAPS]

233
00:15:34,516 --> 00:15:41,148
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

234
00:15:44,443 --> 00:15:45,361
[SIREN BLARES]

235
00:15:45,444 --> 00:15:47,029
Move! Move!

236
00:15:47,112 --> 00:15:54,036
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

237
00:15:56,956 --> 00:15:57,873
[SIREN BLARES]

238
00:15:57,957 --> 00:16:01,835
- [INDISTINCT CHATTER]
- [CAMERA SHUTTERS CLICKING]

239
00:16:01,919 --> 00:16:06,256
- [OFFICER 1] Ma'am, move back.
- [OFFICER 2] It's off-limits.

240
00:16:12,012 --> 00:16:18,811
[INDISTINCT CHATTER]

241
00:16:18,894 --> 00:16:20,562
[REPORTER] Ma'am, what's your name?

242
00:16:20,646 --> 00:16:22,439
What happened inside?

243
00:16:22,523 --> 00:16:25,192
Copy, sir. We'll check the video.

244
00:16:25,275 --> 00:16:26,735
[REPORTER] Are there people who died?

245
00:16:27,778 --> 00:16:29,613
Ma'am, kindly answer our questions.

246
00:16:29,697 --> 00:16:35,828
[UNSETTLING MUSIC PLAYING]

247
00:16:38,372 --> 00:16:40,374
Mrs. Greta Roja, you have to come with us.

248
00:16:42,126 --> 00:16:43,127
Why?

249
00:16:43,711 --> 00:16:46,171
Why? What's going on?

250
00:16:46,255 --> 00:16:49,633
You were identified as the mastermind
behind the La Playa Roja hostage taking.

251
00:16:49,717 --> 00:16:51,844
- That's not true.
- [OFFICER] We have evidence.

252
00:16:51,927 --> 00:16:54,513
- [JERICHO] <i>Don't worry.</i>
- [GRETA] That's not true!

253
00:16:54,596 --> 00:16:56,807
<i>- After the hostage taking…</i>
- No! That's a lie!

254
00:16:56,890 --> 00:16:58,225
<i>…I'll give you your share.</i>

255
00:16:58,308 --> 00:16:59,685
[OFFICER] It's all over the news.

256
00:16:59,768 --> 00:17:01,603
[JERICHO] <i>Ten times the investment.</i>

257
00:17:03,939 --> 00:17:08,527
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

258
00:17:09,945 --> 00:17:10,821
[SIREN BLARES]

259
00:17:10,904 --> 00:17:12,114
Mr. Roja.

260
00:17:12,948 --> 00:17:14,742
The evidence is clear.

261
00:17:15,576 --> 00:17:18,996
Your wife is the mastermind
of the hostage taking.

262
00:17:19,079 --> 00:17:22,583
[MOROSE MUSIC PLAYING]

263
00:17:22,666 --> 00:17:23,667
[MAGNUS GRUNTS]

264
00:17:25,711 --> 00:17:28,881
I think that's impossible, Lieutenant.

265
00:17:30,674 --> 00:17:32,926
You have to come with me, Mr. Roja.

266
00:17:34,053 --> 00:17:35,429
Sir, I'm sorry, but…

267
00:17:37,222 --> 00:17:41,518
shouldn't we first arrest those
who took us hostage

268
00:17:42,269 --> 00:17:43,896
and rescue the hostages?

269
00:17:43,979 --> 00:17:45,773
We're just following orders, Olsen.

270
00:17:47,608 --> 00:17:48,776
And, Mr. Roja,

271
00:17:49,401 --> 00:17:51,653
if your wife is really involved
in all this,

272
00:17:52,696 --> 00:17:54,490
it's possible that you are too.

273
00:17:54,573 --> 00:18:00,162
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

274
00:18:00,245 --> 00:18:02,289
That's why you have to come with us.

275
00:18:02,372 --> 00:18:09,338
[TENSE MUSIC CONTINUES]

276
00:18:10,506 --> 00:18:12,925
- [OFFICER] Just come with us, Mrs. Roja.
- No.

277
00:18:13,842 --> 00:18:15,552
- No! No!
- [OFFICER] Let's go.

278
00:18:15,636 --> 00:18:16,887
I'm not going!

279
00:18:16,970 --> 00:18:17,930
No!

280
00:18:18,555 --> 00:18:20,057
- Ah!
- [OFFICER] Just come with us.

281
00:18:22,226 --> 00:18:24,603
[EMIL]<i> When Jacinto and I were</i>
<i>planning this,</i>

282
00:18:24,686 --> 00:18:30,150
<i>we agreed to just scare the hostages.</i>

283
00:18:30,234 --> 00:18:32,778
<i>He said we shouldn't hurt anybody.</i>

284
00:18:32,861 --> 00:18:34,905
<i>Except for one person.</i>

285
00:18:35,489 --> 00:18:38,742
<i>And then he showed me your picture.</i>

286
00:18:39,326 --> 00:18:41,912
<i>That's when I learned of your background.</i>

287
00:18:41,995 --> 00:18:45,624
<i>No one should get hurt aside from me?</i>

288
00:18:45,707 --> 00:18:48,001
<i>Sounds like Jacinto's very mad at you.</i>

289
00:18:48,085 --> 00:18:49,586
<i>I don't know him!</i>

290
00:18:49,670 --> 00:18:52,381
<i>So why is he targeting you?</i>

291
00:18:52,464 --> 00:18:56,301
<i>Looks like someone has</i>
<i>a lot of anger toward your ex.</i>

292
00:18:56,385 --> 00:18:58,846
<i>Someone connected to Jacinto.</i>

293
00:18:58,929 --> 00:19:01,223
<i>Whoever that is</i>

294
00:19:03,016 --> 00:19:07,646
<i>was also part of orchestrating this mess.</i>

295
00:19:08,939 --> 00:19:15,445
[TENSE MUSIC PLAYING]

296
00:19:21,827 --> 00:19:24,288
<i>Why are you staring at me?</i>
<i>Don't tell me you believe all this.</i>

297
00:19:24,371 --> 00:19:26,999
<i>My father died because of you!</i>

298
00:19:27,624 --> 00:19:29,668
<i>Everyone wants to know why you did that.</i>

299
00:19:29,751 --> 00:19:31,670
[GWEN] <i>Is the tunnel ready?</i>

300
00:19:31,753 --> 00:19:32,713
[MAN] <i>We're almost done.</i>

301
00:19:32,796 --> 00:19:34,756
<i>Let's blow this up.</i>
<i>We're running out of time.</i>

302
00:19:34,840 --> 00:19:36,633
<i>The tunnel will collapse.</i>
<i>We can't do that.</i>

303
00:19:36,717 --> 00:19:38,427
<i>Lucas! Lucas, get out of there!</i>

304
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:41,388
<i>- I got caught! Go!</i>
<i>- Give me that!</i>

305
00:19:41,930 --> 00:19:44,641
[MIKE] <i>I told you that you can't do that!</i>
<i>The soil can't handle the impact.</i>

306
00:19:45,851 --> 00:19:48,020
<i>Why did you do this? Why?!</i>

307
00:19:48,103 --> 00:19:51,315
<i>I was desperate. We're drowning in debt.</i>

308
00:19:51,398 --> 00:19:52,941
<i>- I have to do this, Ma!</i>
<i>- No.</i>

309
00:19:53,025 --> 00:19:54,693
<i>- I'm sorry.</i>
<i>- No, you can't! No!</i>

310
00:19:54,776 --> 00:19:56,528
<i>- You can't do this!</i>
- [BODY THUDS]

311
00:19:59,573 --> 00:20:01,158
<i>Ma! </i>[FRUSTRATED YELL]

312
00:20:02,534 --> 00:20:04,453
- [EXPLOSION]
- [SCREAMING]

313
00:20:04,536 --> 00:20:06,705
[EMIL] <i>Take the bags.</i>
<i>Take the bags now!</i>

314
00:20:06,788 --> 00:20:08,582
[GWEN] <i>Go!</i>
<i>The tunnel will collapse!</i>

315
00:20:08,665 --> 00:20:11,210
[GUNSHOTS]

316
00:20:11,293 --> 00:20:13,212
<i>Let's go this way, baby, okay?</i>

317
00:20:13,295 --> 00:20:14,838
[GUNSHOTS]

318
00:20:17,883 --> 00:20:22,846
[GUNSHOTS]

319
00:20:22,930 --> 00:20:24,014
[EXPLOSION BOOMS]

320
00:20:27,601 --> 00:20:28,977
<i>Olsen!</i>

321
00:20:29,061 --> 00:20:33,065
<i>Baby.</i> [COUGHING]

322
00:20:33,148 --> 00:20:34,942
<i>Mommy, wake up.</i>

323
00:20:35,025 --> 00:20:36,026
<i>Mommy.</i>

324
00:20:37,611 --> 00:20:39,279
<i>Mommy, wake up!</i>

325
00:20:40,113 --> 00:20:41,573
<i>Mommy!</i>

326
00:20:42,199 --> 00:20:43,659
[LIAM] <i>Turn yourself in.</i>

327
00:20:43,742 --> 00:20:46,036
<i>Liam, I'm begging you.</i>

328
00:20:46,119 --> 00:20:47,663
<i>Let's have a fresh start.</i>

329
00:20:47,746 --> 00:20:50,207
<i>You, me, and your father.</i>

330
00:20:50,290 --> 00:20:51,917
<i>Let's go somewhere.</i>

331
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:55,420
<i>Some place where no one knows.</i>

332
00:20:55,504 --> 00:20:57,089
[LIAM, GRETA COUGHING]

333
00:20:57,172 --> 00:20:59,049
<i>- Ma! Ma!</i>
- [GRETA WHIMPERS]

334
00:20:59,132 --> 00:21:00,842
[LIAM HUFFING]

335
00:21:00,926 --> 00:21:02,177
<i>Ma!</i>

336
00:21:02,261 --> 00:21:07,849
[THEME MUSIC PLAYING]
